::Skulletron::

	Skulletron made himself at home in his quarters instantly, and he forgot
all about the little tour that Bloodystrike offered him.  He quickly barged
out of the room and saw Bloodystrike sitting there.

	"Uh, sorry about that.  I guess I was able to settle into my quarters
quicker than I expected.  Well, anyways, back to the tour now!"
